Problem: fugitive files with buf name fugitive:///path/to/file end up having a weird root_dir
Possible solution: Fallback to cwd if bufname path is not found
Drawbacks: new buffers with valid paths that haven't been written yet will end up with "wrong" root_dir

Problem: luals: can't jump to all files
Solution: inject root_dir to workspace.library
Drawbacks: If root_dir is /home/<user>, luals stops working due to too many files.

